name: Senior #27 - Dolores
description:
Dolores is a 79-year-old former organ player in a local rock band who secretly enjoys watching Eurovision, crocheting and crying over Toni Braxton's "Un-Break My Heart”. She is very tough and kindhearted, but can also be very harsh and a bit controlling.

She has a severe phobia of Hello Kitty, and still can’t forget her unrequited high school love, Ronnie, a former video game pirate.
